Mg_supreming_smokenades.


with this map everyone got 1hp and need to throw smoke grenades to the emeny and try to kill them!, u can get a new smoke grenade to get in the teleport below the big arrows. there are 30 spawnpoints for each team so its for a 60 player server.

THE SMOKE WILL FALL TROUGH GROUND SO NO IRRITATING SMOKE U WILL SEE..

IMPORTANT:
The server NEEDS noblock or people get stuck in the teleport!

KOWN THINGS:
With noblock people will stuck there teammates with the smokenades.. but theres no way to fix that?


Map made for the WarmCup community!
